Description: Polyglot task runner with WebAssembly support
 pf-runner is a lightweight, single-file task runner with a symbol-free DSL
 for managing development workflows. It supports:
 .
  - Polyglot shell support (40+ languages)
  - WebAssembly compilation (Rust, C, Fortran, WAT)
  - Build system helpers (Make, CMake, Cargo, etc.)
  - Smart security workflows
  - Container integration
  - Remote execution via SSH
